{"title":"iPadOS 19 will reportedly unlock calligraphy support for Apple Pencil","link":"https://www.macworld.com/article/2787205/ipados-19-will-reportedly-unlock-calligraphy-support-for-apple-pencil.html","date":1747669862000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.macworld.com\">Macworld</a></p>\n\n<div>\n<section><div></div></section>\n\n\n\n<p>In his recent <a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2025-05-19/inside-apple-s-app-store-changes-ios-19-arabic-english-keyboard-apple-pencil-mav1a3jt\">Power On newsletter</a>, Bloomberg’s Mark Gurman reports that Apple is looking to offer a new capability with the Apple Pencil: support for a “virtual reed calligraphy pen” that would make the device a tool for Arabic calligraphy.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A reed pen is also known as a Kamish pen. The “analog” version, if you will, is usually made from river reeds and has been used for centuries by Middle Eastern calligraphers. Apple offers only one type of Pencil tip, and Gurman calls it a “virtual” pen, so it seems that the Arabic calligraphy support will be implemented through software. Gurman doesn’t offer more specifics, so it’s not clear if reed pen support would be for <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/2156898/apple-pencil-compared-1st-2nd-gen-vs-usb-c.html\">all four Apple Pencil models</a> or if it would be limited to the <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/2326113/apple-pencil-pro-m4-m2-ipad-air-pro-features-price-compatibility.html\">Apple Pencil Pro</a> and/or <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/2108888/apple-pencil-usb-c-features-price-comparison-ipad.html\">Apple Pencil (USB-C)</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As part of a larger push to expand its presence in India, Saudi Arabia, and the United Arab Emirates, Apple also has plans to offer a “highly advanced bi-directional keyboard” that can switch between Arabic and English for iOS and iPadOS. Gurman doesn’t state when the pen and the keyboard will be available, though they will likely be part of the new iPadOS 19 announcements at <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/678333/wwdc-ios-macos-watchos-hardware-keynote.html\">WWDC25</a> on June 9.</p>\n\n\n\n\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tApple Pencil Pro\t\t\t\t\t\t</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure><img width=\"2000\" height=\"2000\" alt=\"Apple Pencil Pro\" src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/apple-pencil-pro-product.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t</figure>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tPrice When Reviewed:\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t$129\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tBest Prices Today: \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0D3J71RM7?tag=macworld05-20&amp;linkCode=ogi&amp;th=1&amp;psc=1\" target=\"_blank\">$99 at  Amazon</a><a href=\"https://api.bestbuy.com/click/-/6535042/pdp\" target=\"_blank\">$99 at  Best Buy</a><a href=\"https://www.walmart.com/ip/Apple-Pencil-Pro-Advanced-Tools-Pixel-Perfect-Precision-Tilt-Pressure-Sensitivity-Industry-Leading-Low-Latency-Note-Taking-Drawing-Art-Attaches-Charg/5762417070\" target=\"_blank\">$99 at  Walmart Electronics</a>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\